/-!
# Signed recipe vectors for all-natural complete Hall-Witt schedules

Normalize each bounded affine-term coordinate of the positive-multiplicity
complete transition schedules in the Newton basis.  The remaining all-natural
boundary becomes signed evaluation of two finite cutoff-dependent vectors at
formal predecessor input `-1`.

The file is intentionally not imported by the existing collection proof.
