/-!
# Count-state seed recovery for the successor-repeated nested suffix

The formal predecessor value of the successor-repeated nested transition
schedule is the empty schedule.  This file lifts that transition-word
statement to every cutoff-bounded affine-term coordinate at one common
cutoff-dependent Newton degree bound.

The file is intentionally not imported by the existing collection proof.
