/-!
# Affine endpoint realization of the Hall-Witt packet boundary

The remaining literal outer-packet successor state can be evaluated directly
as the signed Newton value of its actual affine endpoint profile.  This file
records that normalization and packages the remaining positive and negative
obligations as slotwise affine endpoint identities.

The file is intentionally not imported by the existing collection proof.
-/

namespace Submission
namespace TCTex
namespace FAEnd

open WSTrace
open WNTrace
open NPTail
open TBProf
open TACompos
