# Global Newton recipe expansions for Hall-Witt strict tails

The unshifted positive and negative Hall-Witt strict-tail cutoff profiles are
slotwise integer-valued polynomials. Normalize those global profiles directly
in the Newton-binomial basis. Unlike the earlier successor-domain vectors,
these recipes evaluate on the complete natural multiplicity domain, including
