namespace Submission
namespace TCTex
namespace
  RSRecol

open CWTrace
open STSubsti
open
  GPBasis
open
  PRResid
open
  RTResid

universe u


/--
An exact symbolic source for the residual left after removing the canonical
fixed-weight Hall segment from a complete signed Hall-Witt strict tail.

The coefficient may be any function of the symbolic repetition parameter.
The important operational facts are that the source is fixed, truncated,
physically supported in the residual layer, and has the required pointwise
evaluation.
-/
