  intro word hword
  exact
    vocabulary_filtered_reconstructed
      wt hwt x y z cutoff hcutoff coefficient word hword

/--
Once the next parent layer reaches cutoff, every evaluated signed Newton
recipe contribution is removed by physical truncation.
