/-!
# Polynomial bounded terms for complete outer-middle crossing schedules

The complete aligned outer-middle crossing schedule has polynomial
ordered-subsequence coordinates. Every bounded affine-constant coordinate is
a finite producer-refined sum of those coordinates, so its whole bounded term
state is polynomial. The final two lemmas specialize this compiler to the
positive and negative complete first routes.

The file is intentionally not imported by the existing collection proof.
-/

