# Signed-profile form of the Hall-Witt packet affine endpoint kernel

Slotwise Newton evaluation of a supported multiset family commutes with a
fixed affine cutoff-profile transformation after extending the transformation
to integer-valued signed slot profiles.  Apply this to the empty-tail
orbit-swap endpoints.  The remaining packet-local boundary is then exactly:
